{"tid":2402380,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人邏輯力好廢?","createTime":"2021-02-10T11:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T00:31:03.000Z","uid":249170,"like":4,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"08b8311d30720214eda89da48b0c7813925a9681","tid":2402380,"uid":249170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:38:44.000Z","msg":"有冇人邏輯力好廢?<br />\n例如 <br />\n1.阿媽係女人，女人不一定是阿媽<br />\n<br />\n要我套用返男人<br />\n我會覺得<br />\n阿爸係男人，男人都是阿爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 一個箱裝住左個6個橙<br />\n我會覺得呢6個橙比6個箱裝住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.<br />\n2 4 8 16 32 我會覺得之後係 48<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 食兩碗白飯，我食完第一碗 會將第二碗飯倒落第一碗到食，而唔係直接拎第二碗飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 我同A好熟，同B完全唔識<br />\nA大聲叫完我個名，B再叫我名<br />\n我會好奇阿B點解會知我叫咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6.  五個人要選擇有五個號碼<br />\n1，3，4，5號都比人揀左<br />\n我唔會立即諗到我必定會抽中2號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n寫program都係靠撞<br />\n撞到個program run到為止<br />\n<br />\n好處係code editor 永遠唔會恥笑你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會比你撞到run 到為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我呢種邏輯力咁廢既人是否注定失敗，做社會垃圾，老豆老媽生舊屎好過生我，唔死冇撚用...."},{"pid":"1ebb84f926f346c49d64c910c41d742f1a5d82d2","tid":2402380,"uid":197852,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:41:23.000Z","msg":"拎白卡"},{"pid":"ce514dd3a3e1bd421cc1e82b1a748e467855fc37","tid":2402380,"uid":179547,"like":90,"dislike":0,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"呢啲唔叫邏輯力廢，而係叫弱智"},{"pid":"108c3423fe270b3e7ce31acf81acaa2fae4fa479","tid":2402380,"uid":246909,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:42:20.000Z","msg":"唔關邏輯事，智商問題"},{"pid":"b9c226957e3ef1627317be22a8c9b9ec29a47055","tid":2402380,"uid":300420,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MbVsiCc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMbVsiCc.jpg&h=ed5d2059&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"113af987de496650b7201238a342e2f042dd2072","tid":2402380,"uid":80902,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:48:49.000Z","msg":"智商高低同一個人既成就無&quot;必然&quot;關係<br />\n你有毅力同意志力去追求你既目標就會大機會做到, 就好似你寫code咁樣, 花時間既都會寫到, 踏實d唔係咩問題<br />\n<br />\n連登仔好多都聰明反被聰明誤, 以為自己好叻, 走精面, 但最後係一事無成"},{"pid":"8e3dff8bac9454f84d140d9d0764c4edcd2d29f1","tid":2402380,"uid":258097,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T11:49:21.000Z","msg":"去讀discrete math 囉"},{"pid":"7484140d40dbcf213ecdd1d2aa12a005b9c134c3","tid":2402380,"uid":354869,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T12:00:19.000Z","msg":"呢個唔關邏輯事喎，咪亂屈喎<br />\n一睇就知係智商問題"},{"pid":"1664e57567522c038c7fddf2bf6b89d477891e3e","tid":2402380,"uid":21924,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyT